Install dependencies
pip install pymongo python-dotenv flask google-generativeai
Initialize database (character + world)
Run these from the project root:


python scripts/init_character.py
python scripts/init_world.py


Run (CLI)
python core/main.py
Type commands at KERMAN:.
Exit with exit or quit.


Run (Web)
python web/app.py
Open:
http://127.0.0.1:5000
If the web UI is unstable, the CLI flow is the primary development path for now.


